4:
Yahweh says, "Look around, and you will see the people who will be returning from exile!\q1 Your sons will come from distant countries;
\q2 others will carry your little daughters home.
\q1

15:
Previously everyone hated you and ignored you,\q2 but now your city will be majestic forever;
\q1 and I will cause you to be joyful forever.
\q1

19:
And you will no longer need the sun and moon to give you light,\q2 because I, Yahweh, will give you more light than the sun and moon;
\q1 I will be a glorious light for you forever.
\q1
